Package com.chatmotorapi.api.experimental

Provides experimental functionnal APIs like content extraction and content filtering.
These APis may be in future promoted in the com.chatmotorapi.api.functional package or deprecated.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    MotorDefaultContentFilters
    Provides a list of default content filters for use with content filtering functionalities.
    MotorExtractContentRequest
    Handles the creation and execution of a content extraction request using the ChatMotor API.
    MotorExtractContentRequest.Builder
    Builder class for MotorSummaryRequest.
    MotorFilterContentRequest
    Handles the creation and execution of a filer request using the ChatMotor API.
    MotorFilterContentRequest.Builder
    Builder class for MotorSummaryRequest.
